summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 5950 for the improvement of Prosch Avenue West from 13th Avenue West to West Barrett Street; and certain other streets, alleys and avenues; by paving and otherwise improving the same under Ordinance No. 79250, and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
